{"tid":1036043,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"靚仔靚女圍爐區","createTime":"2019-02-25T03:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T15:07:53.000Z","uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"97e558ab668f6e232da9098027d1b72ca9f56859","tid":1036043,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個接近自己都係因為外表<br />\n想改下自己啲性格 問人自己有乜缺點<br />\n但啲人永遠只識奉承話無 無問題 你好好<br />\n淨係會讚我 好辛苦 身邊無人睇到我嘅內在<br />\n明明可以靠個樣呃老襯飯食 都好多人爭住畀錢我使<br />\n但我覺得要靠自己先有意思唔想做雞所以去返工<br />\n但返工好悶 啲同事勁幫手做晒啲嘢<br />\n老細又唔會使我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人生毫無挑戰性覺得自己經已玩完想end game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有諗過整容整醜佢但又對唔住父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無同路人？ \\<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/"},{"pid":"a7ac754a3b2914492107839f2c2a76b648b4a319","tid":1036043,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"dd1e5a21b08484c7b3522c7edf8025833664dbbc","tid":1036043,"uid":232923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"93e17d8b03614721b8c3297543ca224c1830da84","tid":1036043,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"我一照鏡就爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f85dd2777769834408a8a6bad0aee0ec6ede4d","tid":1036043,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"77226b1e07aac45ba17a1048e738e6795c2f6024","tid":1036043,"uid":41139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:11:23.000Z","msg":"癲到呃埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f61c8b2d7f3d292c8264b4c531ddb0e08d1455","tid":1036043,"uid":